OL,3,CZelenskyy weighs in on Reform councils
OL,4,Clowering Ukrainian flags
OL,6,FUkraine's president expressed his hope
OL,7,Fthat they would change their course in
OL,8,Fan interview with the Guardian, which
OL,9,Ftook place in London after he met with
OL,10,FSir Keir Starmer, and the political
OL,11,Fleaders of France and Germany,
OL,12,FEmmanuel Macron and Friedrich Merz.
OL,14,F"I hope they will put it back",
OL,15,FZelenskyy told the newspaper.
OL,17,FHe added: "I don't want to be involved
OL,18,Fin any political things, but you know,
OL,19,Fthe world is so sensitive today.
OL,20,FSometimes little, small mistakes can
OL,21,Fbreak big friendship or huge contacts."
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@^O]yD@KOU}D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
