OL,3,CZelenskyy weighs in on Reform councils
OL,4,Clowering Ukrainian flags
OL,6,FThe Ukrainian leader then suggested
OL,7,Fthat "people have to not make
OL,8,Fmistakes", before adding: "OK, so you
OL,9,Fdid it, please let's come back to the
OL,10,Ftable, let's speak, let's understand
OL,11,Feach other."
OL,13,FElsewhere in the Guardian interview,
OL,14,FZelenskYy stressed how much his
OL,15,Fcountry and Britain need one another
OL,16,Fin Europe's standoff against Russia.
OL,18,F"British people helped us from the
OL,19,Fvery beginning of this war, it's true.
OL,26,@oD@FOUpD@IO]pD@[OUsD@LO]zD@AOU
