OL,3,CZelenskyy weighs in on Reform councils
OL,4,Clowering Ukrainian flags
OL,6,FIt's because of security, not only
OL,7,Fvalues... But it's about security in
OL,8,FEurope. It's in the interests of the
OL,9,FUK," he told said.
OL,11,FZelenskyy also revealed that he plans
OL,12,Fto invite the King for a state visit
OL,13,Fto Ukraine as early as this year,
OL,14,Fafter Charles's show of support for
OL,15,Fhim after US President Donald Trump's
OL,16,Fblistering row with the Ukrainian
OL,17,Fleader in the Oval Office a year ago.
OL,19,FThe King and Zelenskyy met for a
OL,20,Fprivate audience on Monday.
OL,26,@qD@DO]
