OL,3,CZelenskyy weighs in on Reform councils
OL,4,Clowering Ukrainian flags
OL,6,FIn a joint statement on Sunday night,
OL,7,FStarmer, Macron and Merz called on the
OL,8,FRussian president to agree "an
OL,9,Fimmediate and complete ceasefire" and
OL,10,Fcondemned Russia's "large-scale
OL,11,Fmissile and drone attacks" on
OL,12,FUkrainian cities.
OL,14,FOn the same day, a Russian drone
OL,15,Fstrike killed three people waiting at
OL,16,Fa bus stop in south-eastern Ukraine,
OL,17,Fwhile a separate attack damaged a
OL,18,Fstorage centre for spent nuclear fuel
OL,19,Fnine miles from the Chornobyl power
OL,20,Fplant.
